    Source, or modified Covered Source, You may have, to use, reproduce, modify,
    Convey, Make, have Made, and import: a) any Product, and b) anything created
    by using the Product.

5.2 This Licence does not grant any rights in patents that You do not own or
    control, or any rights in trade secrets. Patent licences granted under this
    section 5 may be revoked by the licensor if You initiate patent litigation
    claiming that a Product infringes a patent.

6 Good Practices

6.1 You are encouraged to follow Good Practices in the design, production and
    validation of Products, and to document those practices.

6.2 If You Contribute modifications or additional material to the Covered
    Source, You are encouraged to document these contributions and to provide the
